<BYLINE>
<P>
From Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The search committee screening candidates for the vacant athletic director 
position at Cal State Fullerton has sent the names of three finalists to school 
President Milton Gordon. 
</P>
<P>
 Alan Saltzstein, committee chairman, said it will be Gordon's decision to make 
after the recommendations are reviewed. 
</P>
<P>
 "He will be able to check them out further before a selection is made," 
Saltzstein said. A selection can be expected within two weeks, said Saltzstein, 
who declined to name the three finalists. 
