 The Simpson case: Jay Leno, on prosecutor Marcia Clark visiting the eye doctor 
Monday: "Apparently she got eye strain from rolling her eyes whenever Robert 
Shapiro opened his mouth." 
</P>
<P>
 Leno liked Clark's attire Monday, but adds that she is a very strong woman: "I 
don't want to says she is tough or anything, but I understand that her nickname 
in college was Hillary." 
</P>
