<HEADLINE>
<P>
SERVICES FRIDAY FOR HOLLYWOOD PUBLICIST FOLADARE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Services for Hollywood publicist Maury Foladare are scheduled for 1 p.m. 
Friday at the Church of the Hills in Forest Lawn, Hollywood Hills. Viewing will 
be from 4 to 9 p.m. Thursday at Forest Lawn. Foladare, who represented such 
stars as Bing Crosby and Danny Thomas, died Saturday at the age of 87. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA082494-0111 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 072611 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
