<P>
RUSSIA, CHINA TO SIGN PACT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Russia and China will sign an agreement not to target each other with 
strategic missiles when Chinese President Jiang Zemin visits Moscow from Sept. 
2 to 6, a senior Foreign Ministry official said Tuesday. 
</P>
