 * SCHOOL DISTRICT: Eastside Union School District CAMPUSES BUILT BEFORE 1976: 
Two of three SEISMIC UPGRADES: None INSPECTIONS: None regularly scheduled 
PRECAUTIONS: Program to fasten heavy objects began in March. 
</P>
<P>
