PRECAUTIONS: Furniture/fixtures secured. 
</P>
<P>
 * SCHOOL DISTRICT: Newhall School District CAMPUSES BUILT BEFORE 1976: All 
five SEISMIC UPGRADES: None INSPECTIONS: Annual PRECAUTIONS: 60% of 
furniture/fixtures secured. 
</P>
<P>
 * SCHOOL DISTRICT: Palmdale School District CAMPUSES BUILT BEFORE 1976: Six of 
