<TEXT>
<P>
 1996 Show Date: Action Sports Retailer will be coming home to Long Beach 
Convention Center, but not until 1996.The Times previously reported that the 
show would return in 1995. 
</P>
<P>
 The beach lifestyle and active sports trade show held its first gathering in 
Long Beach in 1980 and moved to San Diego's bay-front convention center in 
1990. The show's promoter, based in South Laguna Beach, plans to hold a Long 
Beach show in February, 1996. 
</P>
</TEXT>
