<P>
 Vans Inc. -- Christopher G. Staff, formerly president and chief operating 
officer of the Speedo and Action Sports divisions of Authentic Fitness Corp. in 
Van Nuys, is joining Vans Inc. in Orange as president and chief executive. An 
article Tuesday misstated his titles. 
